src/
├── app/          (already exists)
├── components/   (for reusable UI components)
├── lib/          (for utility functions and libraries)
├── hooks/        (for custom React hooks)
├── styles/       (for CSS and styling files)
├── utils/        (for helper functions)
├── services/     (for API and external service integrations)
├── context/      (for React Context providers)
├── types/        (for TypeScript types/interfaces if using TS)
└── constants/    (for constant values and configurations) 